#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:19
msgid ""
"Contains global variables accessible from everywhere. Use "
":ref:`get_setting <class_ProjectSettings_method_get_setting>`, "
":ref:`set_setting <class_ProjectSettings_method_set_setting>` or "
":ref:`has_setting <class_ProjectSettings_method_has_setting>` to access "
"them. Variables stored in ``project.godot`` are also loaded into "
"ProjectSettings, making this object very useful for reading custom game "
"configuration options."
msgstr ""
"包含可从任何地方访问的全局变量。使用 :ref:`get_setting "
"<class_ProjectSettings_method_get_setting>`、:ref:`set_setting "
"<class_ProjectSettings_method_set_setting>` 或 :ref:`has_setting "
"<class_ProjectSettings_method_has_setting>` 来访问它们。存储在 ``project.godot`` "
"中的变量，也将加载到 ``项目设置`` 中，从而使该对象，对于读取自定义游戏配置选项非常有用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:21
msgid ""
"When naming a Project Settings property, use the full path to the setting"
" including the category. For example, ``\"application/config/name\"`` for"
" the project name. Category and property names can be viewed in the "
"Project Settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"命名一个项目设置属性时，请使用设置的完整路径，包括类别。例如，``\"application/config/name\"`` "
"用于项目名称。类别和属性名称可以在项目设置对话框中查看。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Overriding:** Any project setting can be overridden by creating a file "
"named ``override.cfg`` in the project's root directory. This can also be "
"used in exported projects by placing this file in the same directory as "
"the project binary."
msgstr ""
"**覆盖**：可以通过在项目的根目录中，创建一个名为 ``override.cfg`` "
"的文件，来覆盖任何项目设置。通过将此文件放置在与项目二进制文件相同的目录中，也可以将其用于导出的项目中。"

