#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:700
msgid ":ref:`bool <class_bool>` **application/boot_splash/fullsize**"
msgstr ":ref:`bool <class_bool>` **application/boot_splash/fullsize**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:706
msgid ""
"If ``true``, scale the boot splash image to the full window length when "
"engine starts. If ``false``, the engine will leave it at the default "
"pixel size."
msgstr "如果为 ``true``，则在引擎启动时，将引导启动图像缩放到整个窗口长度。如果为 ``false``，则引擎会将其保留为默认像素大小。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:712
msgid ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/boot_splash/image**"
msgstr ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/boot_splash/image**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:718
msgid "Path to an image used as the boot splash."
msgstr "用作引导启动画面的图像的路径。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:724
msgid ":ref:`bool <class_bool>` **application/boot_splash/use_filter**"
msgstr ":ref:`bool <class_bool>` **application/boot_splash/use_filter**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:730
msgid ""
"If ``true``, applies linear filtering when scaling the image (recommended"
" for high resolution artwork). If ``false``, uses nearest-neighbor "
"interpolation (recommended for pixel art)."
msgstr "如果为 ``true``，则在缩放图像时应用线性滤波（建议用于高分辨率图稿）。如果为 ``false``，则使用最近相邻插值（建议用于像素图）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:736
msgid ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/config/custom_user_dir_name**"
msgstr ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/config/custom_user_dir_name**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:742
msgid ""
"This user directory is used for storing persistent data (``user://`` "
"filesystem). If left empty, ``user://`` resolves to a project-specific "
"folder in Godot's own configuration folder (see "
":ref:`OS.get_user_data_dir <class_OS_method_get_user_data_dir>`). If a "
"custom directory name is defined, this name will be used instead and "
"appended to the system-specific user data directory (same parent folder "
"as the Godot configuration folder documented in "
":ref:`OS.get_user_data_dir <class_OS_method_get_user_data_dir>`)."
msgstr ""
"该用户目录用于存储持久性数据（``user://`` 文件系统）。如果为空，则 ``user://`` "
"解析为Godot自己的配置文件夹中的项目特定文件夹（参见 :ref:`OS.get_user_data_dir "
"<class_OS_method_get_user_data_dir>`）。如果定义了自定义目录名称，则将使用该名称，并将其追加到系统特定的用户数据目录（与"
" :ref:`OS.get_user_data_dir <class_OS_method_get_user_data_dir>` "
"中记录的Godot配置文件夹，具有相同的父文件夹）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:744
msgid ""
"The :ref:`application/config/use_custom_user_dir "
"<class_ProjectSettings_property_application/config/use_custom_user_dir>` "
"setting must be enabled for this to take effect."
msgstr ""
"必须启用 :ref:`application/config/use_custom_user_dir "
"<class_ProjectSettings_property_application/config/use_custom_user_dir>` "
"设置才能生效。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:750
msgid ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/config/description**"
msgstr ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/config/description**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:756
msgid ""
"The project's description, displayed as a tooltip in the Project Manager "
"when hovering the project."
msgstr "当悬停在项目上时，该项目的描述，在项目管理器中显示为工具提示。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:762
msgid ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/config/icon**"
msgstr ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/config/icon**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:768
msgid ""
"Icon used for the project, set when project loads. Exporters will also "
"use this icon when possible."
msgstr "用于项目的图标，在项目加载时设置。导出器还将在可能的情况下使用此图标。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:774
msgid ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/config/macos_native_icon**"
msgstr ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/config/macos_native_icon**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:780
msgid ""
"Icon set in ``.icns`` format used on macOS to set the game's icon. This "
"is done automatically on start by calling :ref:`OS.set_native_icon "
"<class_OS_method_set_native_icon>`."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:786
msgid ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/config/name**"
msgstr ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/config/name**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:792
msgid ""
"The project's name. It is used both by the Project Manager and by "
"exporters. The project name can be translated by translating its value in"
" localization files."
msgstr "项目的名称。项目管理器和导出器都使用它。可以通过在本地化文件中，翻译其名称来翻译项目名称。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:798
msgid ""
":ref:`String <class_String>` "
"**application/config/project_settings_override**"
msgstr ""
":ref:`String <class_String>` "
"**application/config/project_settings_override**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:804
msgid ""
"Specifies a file to override project settings. For example: "
"``user://custom_settings.cfg``."
msgstr "指定一个文件来覆盖项目设置。例如： ``user://custom_settings.cfg``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:806
msgid ""
"**Note:** Regardless of this setting's value, ``res://override.cfg`` will"
" still be read to override the project settings (see this class' "
"description at the top)."
msgstr "**注意**：不管此设置的值如何，仍然会读取 ``res://override.cfg``，以覆盖项目设置（请参见顶部的该类的说明）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:812
msgid ":ref:`bool <class_bool>` **application/config/use_custom_user_dir**"
msgstr ":ref:`bool <class_bool>` **application/config/use_custom_user_dir**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:818
msgid ""
"If ``true``, the project will save user data to its own user directory "
"(see :ref:`application/config/custom_user_dir_name "
"<class_ProjectSettings_property_application/config/custom_user_dir_name>`)."
" This setting is only effective on desktop platforms. A name must be set "
"in the :ref:`application/config/custom_user_dir_name "
"<class_ProjectSettings_property_application/config/custom_user_dir_name>`"
" setting for this to take effect. If ``false``, the project will save "
"user data to ``(OS user data directory)/Godot/app_userdata/(project "
"name)``."
msgstr ""
"如果为 ``true``，则项目会将用户数据，保存到其自己的用户目录中（参见 "
":ref:`application/config/custom_user_dir_name "
"<class_ProjectSettings_property_application/config/custom_user_dir_name>`）。此设置仅在桌面平台上有效。必须在"
" :ref:`application/config/custom_user_dir_name "
"<class_ProjectSettings_property_application/config/custom_user_dir_name>`"
" 设置中设置一个名称，此名称才能生效。如果为 ``false``，则项目会将用户数据保存到 "
"``（OS用户数据目录）/Godot/app_userdata/（项目名称）`` 中。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:824
msgid ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/config/windows_native_icon**"
msgstr ":ref:`String <class_String>` **application/config/windows_native_icon**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_projectsettings.rst:830
